short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Interactive flight log viewer for Cleanflight

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This is an interactive log viewer for flight logs recorded by Cleanflight's Blackbox feature. It allows logs to be browsed and exported as WebM video.

Please read Cleanflight's Blackbox documentation for more details:

https://github.com/cleanflight/cleanflight/blob/master/docs/Blackbox.md
